Subject: [MSN] Police sketches of suspects who stole a pricey etching
	from a	Michigan Avenue gallery aren't exactly Rembrandts,	but
	authorities are hoping they may help lead them to one.
To: <msn-list@te.verweg.com>
Message-ID: <00fa01c7a726$77252f70$656f8e50$@org>
